  "detailed_description": "Super Rocket Ride is a collaboration between Cosmocat and Unruly Games. It can best be described as a cross between old school lander games and classic platformers of the SNES era: a simple control scheme, lush pixel art, and unforgiving levels fraught with obstacles and hazards.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Analog controls<br></li><li>33 hand-crafted levels<br></li><li>Over-the-top physics-based deaths<br></li><li>Contemporary atmospheric soundtrack featuring music from Snug, JFS and Ogotu</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "Super Rocket Ride is a collaboration between Cosmocat and Unruly Games. It can best be described as a cross between old school lander games and classic platformers of the SNES era: a simple control scheme, lush pixel art, and unforgiving levels fraught with obstacles and hazards.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Analog controls<br></li><li>33 hand-crafted levels<br></li><li>Over-the-top physics-based deaths<br></li><li>Contemporary atmospheric soundtrack featuring music from Snug, JFS and Ogotu</li></ul>",
